{"tid":929631,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"［迷惘] 有冇九龍新界區好獸醫推介？","createTime":"2018-12-05T17:44:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-06T11:26:34.000Z","uid":197568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6878c44ecbbe9155f152038b2132bcc0b41bdfd6","tid":929631,"uid":197568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T17:44:59.000Z","msg":"最近發現我隻狗下體不斷流白色液體<br />\n（貴婦狗女，已絕育，十歲）<br />\n仲有啲異味，佢又成日係到&ldquo;奶&rdquo;個妹妹<br />\n想搵個有良心嘅獸醫睇睇佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上網搵獸醫評價，一係就咸豐年留落<br />\n一係就超級極端<br />\n一係就講啲唔講啲<br />\n一係就比痴線佬騎劫個post<br />\n我真係好迷惘<br />\n<br />\n尤其係好多人話荃灣享和好，但原來荃灣享和又有幾間<br />\n然後npv又好壞參半<br />\n<br />\n小弟仲讀緊書，不直唔多，狗仔又開始老<br />\nafford唔到畀黃綠獸醫呃<br />\n有冇巴絲可以分享下你地覺得好嘅獸醫救救小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n九龍新界區都得<br />\n<br />\n感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63ba148d8e2be82a8e6be04af4ee789f461942c5","tid":929631,"uid":116343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T17:56:12.000Z","msg":"太子npv 不過好難book<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b5514422dce9a79fa55b028764eef96cb40e726","tid":929631,"uid":116343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T18:02:06.000Z","msg":"我隻北京狗仔 十二歲 之前眼睛有事 睇左幾間獸醫診所 反反覆覆都係醫唔好 最後朋友介紹去左npv睇 咁岩book到個有豐富經驗既顧問醫生做左個小手術 最後隻狗仔個眼晴既情況終於穩定返 <br />\n<br />\n同埋npv個價錢應該比一般獸醫診所平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4db560d9a3099cc6d46a44a8bf46387025597419","tid":929631,"uid":136039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T18:03:14.000Z","msg":"認真<br />\nSpca"},{"pid":"bfd8d72a33ddae1bf4f912f073ce9e5c9c8a82bc","tid":929631,"uid":61989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T18:06:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4abef488d6a39138c112a2c27e9ac379d404a284","tid":929631,"uid":171227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T18:10:29.000Z","msg":"荃灣活泉 唔呃錢 醫生都好好"},{"pid":"5ba850c4e4e96db48925497de4416c1b3c47a6f9","tid":929631,"uid":197568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T01:42:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>太子npv 不過好難book<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你都係帶狗仔去睇？"},{"pid":"6fbcd14afb3e81f3175a71ef769c6981a01455a2","tid":929631,"uid":197568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T01:45:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>太子npv 不過好難book<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nChing 都係帶狗仔去睇？"},{"pid":"dda01e1ec16305410d6fb574942dcb0111f143b8","tid":929631,"uid":197568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T01:48:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我隻北京狗仔 十二歲 之前眼睛有事 睇左幾間獸醫診所 反反覆覆都係醫唔好 最後朋友介紹去左npv睇 咁岩book到個有豐富經驗既顧問醫生做左個小手術 最後隻狗仔個眼晴既情況終於穩定返 <br />\n<br />\n同埋npv個價錢應該比一般獸醫診所平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nNpv 聽聞有幾間 你之前邊間？<br />\n<br />\n都有聽過npv平 但又見到都幾多人話佢醫得那西 搞到有啲卻步"},{"pid":"8c3c383dce94460f20470860550205ada70befbd","tid":929631,"uid":197568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T01:50:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>荃灣享和唔係得兩間？<br />\n享和珍禽異獸 同 享和醫療中心（唔記得名）？<br />\n我屋企啲天竺鼠睇開珍禽異獸果邊  啲醫生同護士都好好 <br />\n貓狗果邊就唔清楚了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都好迷惘 上網search 享和獸醫有好幾個result<br />\n照計一般貓狗係咪唔係睇珍禽異獸嗰間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf6fb58a266d59c4c75d6c69acaac561a5e7ccac","tid":929631,"uid":197568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T01:50:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>荃灣活泉 唔呃錢 醫生都好好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有冇睇開邊個獸醫"},{"pid":"5c0eda98b4a14bdadd0fadd685a3fbbe0e229d13","tid":929631,"uid":197568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T01:53:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真<br />\nSpca</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢間我都有望過 介唔介意講多兩句係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53776ccbab5716fe0cb8c55f3a7ae61e37fb70dc","tid":929631,"uid":202254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T02:12:55.000Z","msg":"穩陣嘅 城大獸醫疹所 喺旺角嗰到"},{"pid":"e312d5957538dc9d73e11e480c1fd87611e67a2e","tid":929631,"uid":116343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dda01e1ec16305410d6fb574942dcb0111f143b8","tid":929631,"uid":197568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T01:48:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我隻北京狗仔 十二歲 之前眼睛有事 睇左幾間獸醫診所 反反覆覆都係醫唔好 最後朋友介紹去左npv睇 咁岩book到個有豐富經驗既顧問醫生做左個小手術 最後隻狗仔個眼晴既情況終於穩定返 <br />\n<br />\n同埋npv個價錢應該比一般獸醫診所平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nNpv 聽聞有幾間 你之前邊間？<br />\n<br />\n都有聽過npv平 但又見到都幾多人話佢醫得那西 搞到有啲卻步"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T11:26:34.000Z","msg":"幾間都係同附近幾條街<br />\n<br />\n我隻狗個陣係睇顧問醫生  你可以上佢官網睇下邊個係  同埋我唔知book既時候有無得揀醫生"}]}